subject: Hello Dear,
body:
Hello Dear,
We have finally arranged to deliver your due compensation worth $5.2
Million USD. The Diplomat is already in Lax International Airport in
California, USA with your consignment.We were able to accomplish this
through the help and intervention of INTERNATIONAL MONETARY FUND boss,
Kristalina Georgieva. Every necessary arrangement has been made
successfully with Diplomat Ramos Greg. Contact him quickly with your
delivery information such as 1.Your full name, 2.Your Cellular phone
no, 3.Your home address,4.nearest airport and 
your ID photo
. Contact
him through his email (
ramosgreg569@gmail.com
 ) for more directives.
Yours Sincerely,
Steve Smith

subject: Re: Hello Dear,
body:
Hello Steve Smith,

Wow, that's quite a surprise! I wasn't expecting such news. It's really amazing how you managed to arrange this with the help of Kristalina Georgieva. 

Could you please tell me more about how this came to be? How was my name chosen for this? And who is Diplomat Ramos Greg? Is he someone I should know?

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Ann
